---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const description =
  "Ikhsan is a web developer focused on frontend, who also works across backend and DevOps to support the whole development process";
---

<Base title="About - Ikhsanuddin Syamsuri" description={description}>
  <main
    class="relative isolate overflow-hidden px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:overflow-visible lg:px-0"
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden blur-3xl">
      <svg
        class="absolute left-[max(50%,25rem)] top-0 h-[64rem] w-[128rem] -translate-x-1/2 stroke-gray-200 [mask-image:radial-gradient(64rem_64rem_at_top,white,transparent)]"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        <defs>
          <pattern
            id="e813992c-7d03-4cc4-a2bd-151760b470a0"
            width="200"
            height="200"
            x="50%"
            y="-1"
            patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
          >
            <path d="M100 200V.5M.5 .5H200" fill="none"></path>
          </pattern>
        </defs>
        <svg x="50%" y="-1" class="overflow-visible fill-gray-50">
          <path
            d="M-100.5 0h201v201h-201Z M699.5 0h201v201h-201Z M499.5 400h201v201h-201Z M-300.5 600h201v201h-201Z"
            stroke-width="0"></path>
        </svg>
        <rect
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          stroke-width="0"
          fill="url(#e813992c-7d03-4cc4-a2bd-151760b470a0)"></rect>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <section
      class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-start lg:gap-y-10"
    >
      <div
        class="lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-1 lg:mx-auto lg:grid lg:w-full lg:max-w-7xl lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-x-8 lg:px-8"
      >
        <div class="lg:pr-4">
          <div class="lg:max-w-lg">
            <p class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-orange-600">
              Profile
            </p>
            <h1
              class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 sm:text-4xl"
            >
              Ikhsanuddin Syamsuri
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700">
              Ikhsan is a web developer focused on frontend, who also works
              across backend and DevOps to support the whole development
              process.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="-ml-12 -mt-12 -mr-12 lg:mr-0 p-12 lg:sticky lg:top-4 lg:col-start-2 lg:row-span-2 lg:row-start-1 lg:overflow-hidden"
      >
        <img
          src="https://ik.imagekit.io/ikhsanuddin/profile/ikhsanuddin?tr=w-912"
          alt="Ikhsanuddin Syamsuri"
          width="912"
          height="626"
          class="max-w-none rounded-xl bg-gray-900 shadow-xl ring-1 ring-gray-400/10 w-full"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-2 lg:mx-auto lg:grid lg:w-full lg:max-w-7xl lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-x-8 lg:px-8"
      >
        <div class="lg:pr-4">
          <div
            class="max-w-xl text-base leading-7 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 lg:max-w-lg"
          >
            <p class="mb-8">
              Currently, he mostly builds React.js applications with
              TypeScript. He also loves working with React Native and Vue.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-8">
              His background in psychology and his passion for coding allow him
              to work with data research and process statistical data.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-8">
              In 2012, he started his career in graphic design to help with
              tuition fees in psychology. Since then he has honed his skills in
              digital marketing, analytics, advertisement and SEO (Search
              Engine Optimization).
            </p>

            <ul class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <span>
                  <strong
                    class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
                  >
                    Frontend.
                  </strong>{" "}
                  Next.js is his favorite framework for working with React.js
                  alongside Bootstrap 5, Tailwind, and ANT-Design pattern to
                  develop appealing websites. He sometimes uses Nuxt.js, Vue,
                  Gatsby, and Svelte.
                </span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <span>
                  <strong
                    class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
                  >
                    Backend.
                  </strong>{" "}
                  Nest.js, Go and Laravel are what he prefers, even though he is
                  able to use Java as well.
                </span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <span>
                  <strong
                    class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
                  >
                    Devops.
                  </strong>{" "}
                  Docker is his best friend for deploying applications; since
                  2021 he has been using Kubernetes to manage multiple Docker
                  images and resources.
                </span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <h2
              class="mt-16 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
            >
              No backend? No problem.
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-6">
              He manages to build applications without any backend — for
              prototypes only. We often need a prototype at the early stage of
              the ideation process when calling for investment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section
      class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-start lg:gap-y-10"
    >
      <div
        class="lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-2 lg:row-start-1 lg:mx-auto lg:grid lg:w-full lg:max-w-7xl lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-x-8 lg:px-8"
      >
        <ol class="border-l border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-500">
          <li>
            <div class="flex-start flex items-center pt-3">
              <div
                class="-ml-[8px] mr-3 h-[15px] w-[15px] rounded-full bg-neutral-400"
              >
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                April 2023, IT department disbanded
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3 ml-4 mt-2">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">TwoSpaces</h3>
              <a
                class="text-orange-600"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                href="https://twospacesgroup.com"
              >
                twospacesgroup.com
              </a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="flex-start flex items-center pt-2">
              <div
                class="-ml-[5px] mr-3 h-[9px] w-[9px] rounded-full bg-neutral-300 dark:bg-neutral-500"
              >
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                April 2022
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-6 ml-4 mt-2">
              <h4 class="mb-1 mt-3 font-semibold">Lead Software Engineer</h4>
              <p class="mb-3 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Building digital property management services. Reservation,
                booking chart, payment, room service, email service, API
                integration with Channel Manager and digital check-in were
                built within a year.
              </p>
              <p class="mb-3 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Mentoring, reporting, code review, distributing tasks and
                giving support were his day-to-day job as a lead of 2 backend
                engineers, 1 frontend engineer, 1 database admin and quality
                assurance.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li>
            <div class="flex-start flex items-center pt-2">
              <div
                class="-ml-[8px] mr-3 h-[15px] w-[15px] rounded-full bg-neutral-400"
              >
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                April 2022, left
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3 ml-4 mt-2">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Indotek Sukses Sekawan</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                formerly Tekno Kreasi Nyata
              </p>
              <a
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-orange-600"
                href="https://indotek.github.io"
              >
                indotek.github.io
              </a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="flex-start flex items-center pt-2">
              <div
                class="-ml-[5px] mr-3 h-[9px] w-[9px] rounded-full bg-neutral-300 dark:bg-neutral-500"
              >
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                May 2021
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3 ml-4 mt-2">
              <h4 class="mb-1 mt-3 font-semibold">Lead Software Engineer</h4>
              <p class="mb-3 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Maintained development, gave level-3 support, and reported for
                a B2B white-label product with single-tenant software, managed
                in multi-tenant infrastructure using Kubernetes. The tools we
                used were Jira Agile, Google Cloud Platform, Stackdriver,
                Google Tag Manager and Google Analytics.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li>
            <div class="flex-start flex items-center pt-2">
              <div
                class="-ml-[5px] mr-3 h-[9px] w-[9px] rounded-full bg-neutral-300 dark:bg-neutral-500"
              >
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                April 2019
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4 mt-2 mb-3">
              <h4 class="mb-1 mt-3 font-semibold">Lead Frontend Engineer</h4>
              <p class="mb-3 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                The frontend team got bigger, so he was promoted to lead the
                team. Deciding the stack for the next project and team capacity
                management became his responsibility. Leading 4 people.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li>
            <div class="flex-start flex items-center pt-2">
              <div
                class="-ml-[5px] mr-3 h-[9px] w-[9px] rounded-full bg-neutral-300 dark:bg-neutral-500"
              >
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                November 2018
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4 mt-2 mb-6">
              <h4 class="mb-1 mt-3 font-semibold">Senior Frontend Engineer</h4>
              <p class="mb-3 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Developed websites using React.js with ANT-Design for back
                office and Vue/Nuxt.js for starting the project. He also
                mentored his colleagues.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li>
            <div class="flex-start flex items-center pt-2">
              <div
                class="-ml-[8px] mr-3 h-[15px] w-[15px] rounded-full bg-neutral-400"
              >
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                February 2019, left
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3 ml-4 mt-2">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Coconutlab, Ltd</h3>
              <a
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-orange-600"
                href="https://coconutlab.io"
              >
                coconutlab.io
              </a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="flex-start flex items-center pt-2">
              <div
                class="-ml-[5px] mr-3 h-[9px] w-[9px] rounded-full bg-neutral-300 dark:bg-neutral-500"
              >
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Sept 2018
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-6 ml-4 mt-2">
              <h4 class="mb-1 mt-3 font-semibold">Senior Frontend Engineer</h4>
              <p class="mb-3 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Developed a mobile app using React Native and managed to ship
                the application to production level.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li>
            <div class="flex-start flex items-center pt-2">
              <div
                class="-ml-[8px] mr-3 h-[15px] w-[15px] rounded-full bg-neutral-400"
              >
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Sept 2018, left
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3 ml-4 mt-2">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">YAMISOK</h3>
              <a
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-orange-600"
                href="https://yamisok.com"
              >
                yamisok.com
              </a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="flex-start flex items-center pt-2">
              <div
                class="-ml-[5px] mr-3 h-[9px] w-[9px] rounded-full bg-neutral-300 dark:bg-neutral-500"
              >
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                June 2017
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3 ml-4 mt-2">
              <h4 class="mb-1 mt-3 font-semibold">Senior Frontend Engineer</h4>
              <p class="mb-3 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Decided to follow the frontend path. He rebuilt the website
                using Vue.js and the new Bootstrap 4, and took on a new
                responsibility as a senior frontend engineer: mentorship.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="flex-start flex items-center pt-2">
              <div
                class="-ml-[5px] mr-3 h-[9px] w-[9px] rounded-full bg-neutral-300 dark:bg-neutral-500"
              >
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                May 2016
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3 ml-4 mt-2">
              <h4 class="mb-1 mt-3 font-semibold">Junior Software Engineer</h4>
              <p class="mb-3 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Translating Photoshop designs into HTML and CSS was his main
                job. Using Bootstrap 3, he created a gamer portal for online
                tournaments including upper and lower bracket systems, feeds,
                realtime chat, and marketing email. Sometimes he helped other
                colleagues with the Laravel backend.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
